it&#039;s like sex offender registry. everyone knows it&#039;s a flawed system that does more harm then good and actually increases the likelyhood of reoffending. but no one that actually matters will speak out against it because if they do they &quot;support sex offenders&quot; 

if anyone at riot were to speak out against how problematic the report system actually is. they would be labled as &quot;supporting toxic players&quot; and probably be fired
